---
title: Creamy Rosé Shrimp and Tortellini with Roasted Red Peppers
description: This one is just like your favourite restaurant's cheesy shrimp tortellini! The creamy rosé sauce coats every piece of pasta and the gooey mozzarella cheese makes for an unforgettable takeout fake-out.
